Package: ClaudeAgentSDK
Title: R SDK for Claude Code Agent
Version: 0.1.4
Authors@R: person("ClaudeAgentSDK", "Authors", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "sdk@example.com")
Description: R implementation of the Claude Agent SDK. Spawns the Claude Code CLI
    as a subprocess and communicates via newline-delimited JSON stream protocol,
    including the full bidirectional control protocol (permission requests, hooks,
    interrupt). Mirrors the Python claude-agent-sdk API.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.0
Imports:
    processx (>= 3.8.0),
    jsonlite,
    R6,
    later,
    coro,
    rlang (>= 1.0.0),
    cli
Suggests:
    promises,
    shiny,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    withr
SystemRequirements: Claude Code CLI (>= 2.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
